WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: bHSHlyZHZpc

NOTE Language: en

00:03:47.333 --> 00:03:51.088
﻿So, this is to thank you all for

00:03:51.718 --> 00:03:54.260
helping in building this house

00:03:56.743 --> 00:03:58.900
and making it so beautiful.

00:04:01.890 --> 00:04:03.780
All the thankfulness

00:04:05.437 --> 00:04:07.186
is from

00:04:08.061 --> 00:04:10.374
us, both of us, to you.

00:04:13.331 --> 00:04:14.937
Today is a very

00:04:15.138 --> 00:04:17.643
interesting day when

00:04:17.843 --> 00:04:21.660
you are worshipping the Gruhalakshmi here,

00:04:22.424 --> 00:04:24.700
means the Gruhalakshmi of this house.

00:04:25.823 --> 00:04:27.424
In the same way

00:04:28.650 --> 00:04:32.106
in your family also, in your houses, homes you must

00:04:32.306 --> 00:04:34.196
do Gruhalakshmis’ puja.

00:04:35.327 --> 00:04:37.316
The woman has to be

00:04:37.517 --> 00:04:39.528
the Gruhalakshmi herself

00:04:40.472 --> 00:04:42.672
and then she should be worshipped.

00:04:43.405 --> 00:04:46.355
“Yatya naria pujyante, tatra bhramante Devata.”

00:04:46.556 --> 00:04:48.780
Where the women are respected

00:04:48.980 --> 00:04:51.522
and worshipped there

00:04:52.527 --> 00:04:55.155
reside all the deities.

00:04:55.356 --> 00:04:57.460
But they should be respectable also.

00:04:57.660 --> 00:04:59.828
If they are not respectable

00:05:00.028 --> 00:05:02.536
then the deities won’t reside there.

00:05:02.737 --> 00:05:04.315
So, it’s a big responsibility

00:05:04.515 --> 00:05:06.740
on a Gruhalakshmi to be respectable

00:05:06.940 --> 00:05:09.859
so that all the deities are happy in the family.

00:05:10.059 --> 00:05:12.300
And once she is respected,

00:05:12.500 --> 00:05:15.860
she will try to be respectable also.

00:05:16.060 --> 00:05:17.580
So, the respect

00:05:17.780 --> 00:05:20.399
of the Gruhalakshmi is very important.

00:05:22.593 --> 00:05:24.180
Today

00:05:25.389 --> 00:05:28.620
we are having this little puja

00:05:28.821 --> 00:05:30.826
from all the builders

00:05:31.026 --> 00:05:33.031
who helped us here,

00:05:33.420 --> 00:05:35.499
with the blessings of Vishwakarma

00:05:35.700 --> 00:05:37.368
and Brahmadeva;

00:05:37.569 --> 00:05:39.718
those who have tried

00:05:40.055 --> 00:05:43.255
to make this house so beautiful.

00:05:44.811 --> 00:05:48.315
Also, as you know, Blake has described this house.

00:05:48.515 --> 00:05:51.060
It has a special significance

00:05:51.736 --> 00:05:54.198
and we have to now

00:05:54.398 --> 00:05:56.060
hand it over to somebody else,

00:05:56.800 --> 00:06:00.700
the one who will appreciate and respect this house;

00:06:01.155 --> 00:06:04.500
who will understand the value and worth of this house.

00:06:04.860 --> 00:06:07.283
And for that we have to pray

00:06:07.483 --> 00:06:09.802
that it will be sold to such a person

00:06:10.003 --> 00:06:13.804
who is a person who will be

00:06:14.005 --> 00:06:17.807
a connoisseur, a person who will understand

00:06:18.008 --> 00:06:20.980
the depth and the

00:06:22.009 --> 00:06:23.660
aesthetics

00:06:24.422 --> 00:06:26.260
of this place

00:06:27.031 --> 00:06:30.387
and the one who will be paying for that,

00:06:30.841 --> 00:06:32.369
valuing that.

00:06:33.133 --> 00:06:34.820
So, we have to ask

00:06:35.020 --> 00:06:36.700
for such a blessing.

00:06:41.451 --> 00:06:44.142
Of course, one should not get attached to anything.

00:06:44.342 --> 00:06:46.180
Whatever is created,

00:06:46.951 --> 00:06:49.364
is created. One should never be attached.

00:06:49.564 --> 00:06:51.180
Because we have done this, so

00:06:51.380 --> 00:06:54.780
we should be attached to it, is not the way a Sahaja

00:06:55.343 --> 00:06:56.877
Yogi should think about it.

00:06:57.078 --> 00:07:00.162
But one should think about that,
now we have created something beautiful

00:07:00.362 --> 00:07:02.140
we can recreate another thing

00:07:02.340 --> 00:07:05.283
and we can produce other better things.

00:07:05.483 --> 00:07:06.780
That’s how an artist

00:07:06.980 --> 00:07:09.617
can go on producing and producing.

00:07:09.818 --> 00:07:11.100
Of course,

00:07:11.300 --> 00:07:13.820
there’s one thing: that if there is

00:07:14.170 --> 00:07:17.060
within us the joy,

00:07:19.979 --> 00:07:23.013
then only you produce joy.

00:07:23.214 --> 00:07:25.540
If there is no joy you cannot.

00:07:27.194 --> 00:07:28.900
So first of all

00:07:29.100 --> 00:07:31.330
before doing any work

00:07:31.531 --> 00:07:33.191
creating anything

00:07:33.620 --> 00:07:35.420
one must measure up

00:07:35.980 --> 00:07:37.820
the amount of

00:07:39.224 --> 00:07:41.138
joy one has received,

00:07:41.338 --> 00:07:44.496
the blessings one has received from the Divine,

00:07:44.902 --> 00:07:46.500
and then recreate.

00:07:46.700 --> 00:07:50.044
With that consciousness, with that awareness

00:07:50.245 --> 00:07:52.620
you’ll find your creation will be very beautiful.

00:07:52.820 --> 00:07:56.109
And we have to bring the world to a new

00:07:56.999 --> 00:07:59.620
method of creativity

00:08:00.235 --> 00:08:02.460
where there is exuberance,

00:08:02.872 --> 00:08:04.580
exuberance,

00:08:05.273 --> 00:08:08.691
of joy and

00:08:09.676 --> 00:08:13.300
of Divine aesthetics,

00:08:14.443 --> 00:08:17.288
because the world is going from bad to worse.

00:08:17.553 --> 00:08:20.756
I find nowadays people may just like to have

00:08:20.980 --> 00:08:24.700
some sort of a white cloth hanging and calling it a painting.

00:08:25.268 --> 00:08:27.804
That’s not a painting because there is nothing inside.

00:08:28.005 --> 00:08:30.660
It has become hollow, empty; there’s nothing inside,

00:08:30.860 --> 00:08:32.656
so that there is no exuberance.

00:08:32.857 --> 00:08:34.437
So, to recreate that,

00:08:34.637 --> 00:08:36.983
you people have to

00:08:37.874 --> 00:08:39.891
desire and ask for it,

00:08:40.091 --> 00:08:41.991
and we’ll have people of that kind.

00:08:42.192 --> 00:08:43.858
It is just to be desired,

00:08:44.058 --> 00:08:46.180
and you all should desire for such things:

00:08:46.584 --> 00:08:49.780
that people of exuberance should come forward

00:08:49.980 --> 00:08:53.680
to value such things which are full of joy.

00:08:55.232 --> 00:08:56.700
May God bless you.

00:09:01.766 --> 00:09:05.166
And so what is this, first the Ganesha puja we’ll do?

00:41:43.487 --> 00:41:45.264
May God bless you all.

00:41:51.171 --> 00:41:52.979
May God bless this house.

00:41:53.179 --> 00:41:56.040
May God bless Mr. Shrivastava.

