If you eat all these things. I have done such a good cooking!

00:55:54.113 --> 00:55:56.943
I have to say you shouldn’t eat anything anymore

00:55:57.143 --> 00:55:59.647
because if you eat it then I’ll just vibrate it,

00:55:59.847 --> 00:56:03.700
but you people don’t eat anything
now because such a lot has been cooked,

00:56:03.900 --> 00:56:05.460
OK?

00:56:06.715 --> 00:56:08.519
Such nice food.

00:56:56.708 --> 00:56:59.199
More than that, ahead of that.

