how God

00:57:19.693 --> 00:57:23.117
does little, little things to please the bhaktas.

00:57:24.593 --> 00:57:26.500
And it’s a very good

00:57:26.813 --> 00:57:28.940
thing which you’ll like it very much;

00:57:29.140 --> 00:57:30.620
which were -

